{"about_the_game":"<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Launch yourself to the top and defy gravity</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Ring Toss is a challenging 2D game where you play as a ring with a single goal: to reach the top. Every throw matters, and every move will either bring you closer to success\u2026 or send you back to the start. With precise physics-based mechanics, you\u2019ll need to calculate angles, adjust your strength, and perfect your skills to navigate a world full of platforms and obstacles.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Designed with detailed pixel art graphics and a focus on mechanical simplicity, Ring Toss delivers an experience that\u2019s easy to pick up but hard to master. Are you ready for the challenge?</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>Key Features</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Physics-based mechanics</strong>: Throw, bounce, and adjust your trajectory. Mastering the throw is essential to progress.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Pixel art graphics</strong>: A vibrant and carefully designed visual style that enhances every level.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Challenging gameplay</strong>: A design that rewards precision and perseverance. Every mistake is a chance to learn and improve.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong>Steady progression</strong>: Levels crafted to gradually increase in difficulty, testing your skill and patience.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340760/extras/GIF_01.gif?t=1735550214\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340760/extras/GIF_02.gif?t=1735550214\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3340760/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735550214","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/st